%TAG !u! tag:unity3d.com,2011:
--- !u!114 &11400000
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: e9620f8c34305754d8cc9a7e49e852d9, type: 3}
  m_Name: LocalTable_en
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Unity.Localization::UnityEngine.Localization.Tables.StringTable
  m_LocaleId:
    m_Code: en
  m_SharedData: {fileID: 11400000, guid: aac8ceb655d3e9940afa077145e80ad1, type: 2}
  m_Metadata:
    m_Items: []
  m_TableData:
  - m_Id: 10001
    m_Localized: As the cold, damp scent of earth fills my senses, it seems that
      even death is denied to me.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 10002
    m_Localized: Not a shred of flesh remains, leaving only these crumbling shards
      of bone to sustain my existence.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 10003
    m_Localized: How dare you, contemptible beast, desecrate the hallowed grounds
      where my kin find their eternal rest.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 10004
    m_Localized: "I will not allow your foul fangs to profane the sanctity of my
      kin\u2019s remains."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 10005
    m_Localized: "I\u2019ll end you where you stand!"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 10006
    m_Localized: It feels as though the touch of those tiny hands, which brushed
      against mine in the flames, still lingers on my fingertips.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 10007
    m_Localized: You dare defile this ground.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 10008
    m_Localized: Silence, you foul creature. I shall flay your wretched hide to appease
      the souls of my kin.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 10009
    m_Localized: No warmth persists. All that remains of my child is this cold fragment...
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 10010
    m_Localized: The guilt of failing to protect my child weighs heavily on my bones.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 10011
    m_Localized: Do not weep, my child. I will pass judgment and offer up a blood
      sacrifice for your sorrow.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 10012
    m_Localized: It is the only reason I awoke from the dead.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 20001
    m_Localized: Grrr... The Grim Reaper has confirmed that your life has ended...
      The screams you let out as that intense hatred is crushed must be all the sweeter.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 20002
    m_Localized: No more screams. Only the sound of your end.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 20003
    m_Localized: Grrr... A rattling skull! The screams from that day continue to
      echo in my ears. How could you possibly pursue revenge alone?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 20004
    m_Localized: Tell the Grim Reaper. "Now, I rise to crush your wretched world."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 20005
    m_Localized: First, I shall stain this barren land with your crimson blood
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 20006
    m_Localized: "Arrogant worm! I\u2019ll grind your spite to dust. No rest for
      you. Ever!"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 20007
    m_Localized: Grrr... I'll trample that rusty crown and turn this place into a
      proper slaughterhouse!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 20008
    m_Localized: Abominable malice stains the silence of my frost. A king whose soul
      was torn by Death itself... why do you still haunt the living with your cold
      breath?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 20009
    m_Localized: The tears of my people still soak the ground. Until those tears
      freeze into icicles and pierce right through you, I cannot hold my breath.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 20010
    m_Localized: Foolish creature. You dare defy the sanctity of death for a mere
      grudge? This time, I shall freeze your very spite until it shatters into a
      thousand shards.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 20011
    m_Localized: Speak not of providence. Here, only my vengeance and your end remain.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 20012
    m_Localized: "Crowned phantom! I shall begin by freezing those arrogant eyes
      of yours. This is my domain\u2014where neither the living nor the dead are
      permitted to linger!"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 20013
    m_Localized: (Black mist splits. and there, Death emerges, trailing a colossal
      scythe behind.)
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 20014
    m_Localized: "At last, You\u2019ve crossed the line, King of a fallen realm."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 20015
    m_Localized: Defier of eternal rest... tell me, is such a wretched grudge all
      that fuels your hollow stride?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 20016
    m_Localized: Rest? Did you grant them rest while your scythe reaped their souls?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 20017
    m_Localized: I refused to die just so I could rip out your hollow eyes and drown
      them in the hell I survived.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 20018
    m_Localized: "What a truly futile obsession! The fall of the kingdom and the
      decline of its people\u2026 It is the natural order of things, no different
      from water flowing to the depths. You, too, were nothing more than a single
      ripple in that current."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 20019
    m_Localized: I returned to shatter that providence. On the day my crown was shattered
      and my heart was broken, I was no longer human.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 20020
    m_Localized: Now, only your head to fall, and your world to crumble.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 20021
    m_Localized: Pitiable soul. I shall teach thee the brevity of thy wrath. Time
      will swallow up your grandiose desire for revenge and your name, leaving them
      forever lost in the silence of nothingness.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 20022
    m_Localized: Before time runs out, I will hear your screams. This place will
      not be the grave of the souls you have taken, but your own grave.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 20023
    m_Localized: The moment the Grim Reaper falls, the darkness shatters into a thousand
      shards.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 20024
    m_Localized: As the burning thirst for vengeance fades, the phantom world sustained
      by the King's obsession dissolves... returning at last to the stillness of
      its original grave.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 20025
    m_Localized: "From within the King\u2019s breast, the shards of the Princess\u2019s
      soul spill forth, weaving a form of pure radiance. Amidst the glow, she appears\u2014folding
      her father's skeletal frame into a tender embrace."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 20026
    m_Localized: No more, my Lord. Yield your heavy steel, and find your solace in
      peace.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 20027
    m_Localized: "At the touch of the Princess\u2019s voice, the bitter malice and
      obsession that held the King captive are washed away."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 20028
    m_Localized: No longer consumed by blind vengeance, he returns to himself. not
      as a wraith of war, but as the King of Serilda, preparing for his peaceful
      rest.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 20029
    m_Localized: Yes... It was a very long dream...
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 20030
    m_Localized: At last, I can rest.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 20031
    m_Localized: The obsession has lifted, and the dawn has broken at last. May you
      find a place where your hands need never touch a blade again
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 20032
    m_Localized: At last... even the flame of this life flickers out, leaving its
      great purpose to the ashes.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 20033
    m_Localized: Even the searing malice of your vengeance scatters now as frozen
      ash. this moment, as it returns, pierces my heart with a chilling sorrow.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 30001
    m_Localized: The forge still burns. To reach the end of my vengeance, I must
      be armed in cruelty.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 30002
    m_Localized: '[Sharpen the blade keenly.]'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 30003
    m_Localized: A finer edge. One strike, one silence.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 30004
    m_Localized: '[enhance the rusted armor.]'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 30005
    m_Localized: Shed this rusted plate. I must refit it to my very bones. Hard enough
      to deny a counterattack.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 30006
    m_Localized: You have come, my Lord... Even in this freezing darkness, we waited
      only for the sound of your footsteps.\n The failure was ours, My Lord. Do not
      let guilt stay your hand. Please keep moving forward.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 30007
    m_Localized: '[Heal the wounds with the breath of the people.]'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 30008
    m_Localized: Cease your sorrow. Let our fading lives mend your broken spirit.
      Stand tall once more, and lead us forward.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 30009
    m_Localized: '[Consecrate the life force of the people to the heart.]'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 30010
    m_Localized: My Lord... take our final breath of life. Though our souls scatter
      to the wind, let us become your heart and fill the vessel. Do not let your
      spirit break.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 30011
    m_Localized: Dusty treaties remain. Though the flesh is gone, the tactical gambits
      that shook the battlefield must be reawakened.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 30012
    m_Localized: 'Tactics: Swift Move.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 30013
    m_Localized: "A swift strike. A masterpiece of war\u2014leaving no room for reaction."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 30014
    m_Localized: 'Tactics: Rapid Volley.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 30015
    m_Localized: "The flow of the fray. One strike to feed the next\u2014a relentless
      chain of slaughter."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 30016
    m_Localized: "A long, weary road you\u2019ve walked... Hehehe... You look so
      tired, my poor, broken King. \\n I see it clinging to your straight back...
      a bitter loneliness and a thirst for vengeance. Won't you stay a while and
      ask this old crone for the way?"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 30017
    m_Localized: '[Seek the old woman''s advice.]'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 30018
    m_Localized: "My poor, pitied King... Listen to this old crone's whispers. Your
      guard may grow frail and your armor thin, but in exchange, I shall teach you
      a ruinous gambit\u2014one that will drive your blade deep into the very heart
      of your foe."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 30019
    m_Localized: '[Embrace the old woman.]'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 30020
    m_Localized: "Hehehe... Yes, my pitied King. Sink deeper into these withered
      arms. I shall take half the life that sustains you, but in return, I will make
      those dry bones strike with a speed you\u2019ve never known."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 30021
    m_Localized: Even under a shattered sky, you seek a path. Your light has fallen,
      yet a single chance lingers in the warped orbit. Shall I unveil it?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 30022
    m_Localized: '[Overlap the threads of fate.]'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 30023
    m_Localized: The stars have crossed. Fate flows through your steel, and soon,
      a moment of unpredictable power shall unfurl. Will you place your faith in
      the luck of the high heavens?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 30024
    m_Localized: '[Glimpse the twisted timeline.]'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 30025
    m_Localized: A fractured future... Your steps grow heavy, but your blade now
      bears a second destiny. Every strike carries a shard of cruel fate. The price
      is yours to bear.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 30026
    m_Localized: "To step into this ruin... my broken Lord, if my prayer can bring
      even a moment\u2019s rest to your shattered frame, I shall gladly bless the
      path you tread"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 30027
    m_Localized: '[Receive the Martyr''s prayer.]'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 30028
    m_Localized: May this prayer be a flicker of light upon your path. Though the
      power to heal your wounds may wane, the weight of your soul that you can now
      bear will be deeper and broader than ever before.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 30029
    m_Localized: '[Take the remaining divine power.]'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 30030
    m_Localized: Nothing but hollow screams here. Your maximum life will wither,
      yet the holy grace mending your wounds shall blaze with unrivaled intensity.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 30031
    m_Localized: 'Spiteful phantom, wandering the dark... I grant the strength you
      crave. Yet remember: what the hand takes, the soul must repay.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 30032
    m_Localized: '[Accept the angel''s merciful touch.]'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 30033
    m_Localized: Your yearning shall be the light. when your HP drops below half,
      the Sacred Touch will reach deeper into your wounds.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 30034
    m_Localized: '[Don the angel''s holy protection.]'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 30035
    m_Localized: Full of energy is your steadfast shield. While your form is whole,
      a Heavenly Aegis shall bolster you.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 30036
    m_Localized: "Keke... Your searing heart led me here. Your soul\u2019s ruin is
      nothing to me. You want the power for revenge? Then pay the price. A life for
      a life, a soul for a soul."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 30037
    m_Localized: '[Contract with the demon.]'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 30038
    m_Localized: Very well. When you dance with death, your blade shall unleash a
      cataclysm. Enjoy your ruinous power. The deal is done.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 30039
    m_Localized: '[Offer vitality to the demon.]'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 30040
    m_Localized: I take your life as my tribute. In exchange, I shall grant you a
      fearsome speed. That fleeting moment will be your final, dying flame.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 30041
    m_Localized: The wind has shifted... To think a pulsing heart still beats in
      this barren land. The children of the forest are curious about your wounded
      soul. Will you accept their playful blessing?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 30042
    m_Localized: '[Absorb the spirit''s vital flow.]'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 30043
    m_Localized: Heed the river of life. Breathe in the grace that nature yields.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 30044
    m_Localized: Be promised the forest's last protection.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 30045
    m_Localized: The forest promises protection. As your light fades, the spirits
      will ignite their souls to bring you back. A miracle granted but once.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 40001
    m_Localized: My Lord... even death could not hold your grievance.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 40002
    m_Localized: Can you feel it, My Lord? The unseen hand that guides you... an
      inescapable pull within this wretched wheel.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 40003
    m_Localized: My Lord... let this be your final journey. To the rest you so rightly
      earned.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 40004
    m_Localized: Remember, my Lord. Though your flesh is gone, the royal power carved
      into your soul still breathes within this grid.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 40005
    m_Localized: Seize a shard of thought and slide it aside. That fleeting shift
      shall decide your destiny.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 40006
    m_Localized: Be wary. A false judgment will only gnaw at his remaining breath.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 40007
    m_Localized: With every shard you shift, the shattered soul will slowly fade.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 40008
    m_Localized: Match three or more shards of the same hue to shatter them. That
      fleeting union shall ignite a flame of destruction to consume your foes.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 40009
    m_Localized: "The clock ticks with every move. As you finish your strike with
      the shards, the enemy\u2019s blade draws near. Do not be reckless."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 40010
    m_Localized: The red shards are your piercing steel. Align them to strike a mortal
      blow.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 40011
    m_Localized: Blue shards are your shield. Align them to block their malice.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 40012
    m_Localized: Pink shards are your broken heart. Align them to mend your fading
      life.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 40013
    m_Localized: Green shards are your royal arts. Align them to prepare a surging
      tide.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 50001
